metadata.name: Matthew Oworu - 2022 Canada 7s Season Highlights
metadata.description:
Matthew Owuru is a promising young rugby talent, born in Calgary, Canada, in 2000.  Growing up in Canada, Basketball was his first love, followed by football. Sports have always been part of his life. 
His athletic acumen really kicked in when his family moved to Zimbabwe, where he started to pick up the game of rugby.
On the  2nd of July 2022, Matt received his first Rugby 7s Cap for the Canada National Team - its only up from here!
